<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{HeaderTitle}}</title>
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body { font-family: 'Nunito', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    </style>
</head>
<body style="margin: 0; padding: 20px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f7ff 0%, #faf8ff 100%); min-height: 100vh;">
    <div style="max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: white; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(112, 66, 148, 0.12);">
        <!-- Header with Premium Gradient -->
        <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #704294 0%, #8b5cf6 50%, #c5468e 100%); color: white; padding: 40px 30px; text-align: center; position: relative;">
            <div style="position: absolute; top: 0; right: 0; opacity: 0.1; font-size: 120px; line-height: 1;">✉</div>
            <h1 style="margin: 0; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.5px; position: relative; z-index: 1;">{{HeaderTitle}}</h1>
            <p style="margin: 8px 0 0 0; font-size: 14px; opacity: 0.95; position: relative; z-index: 1;">Welcome to Your Professional Email Management Platform</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Main Content -->
        <div style="padding: 40px 30px; line-height: 1.8; color: #495057;">
            <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 15px;">Hello <span style="color: #704294; font-weight: 700;">{{Username}}</span>,</p>

            <p style="font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px;">Welcome to <strong style="color: #704294;">TPMailer</strong>! We're excited to have you on board.</p>

            <p style="font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 25px;">Your account has been successfully activated. You can now access our sophisticated email service platform to manage your email integrations with ease and confidence.</p>

            <!-- Success Badge -->
            <div style="margin: 25px 0; padding: 16px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e8f5e9 0%, #f1f8f6 100%); border: 1px solid #a5d6a7; border-left: 4px solid #4caf50; border-radius: 8px;">
                <div style="color: #2e7d32; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 6px;">✓ Account Activated</div>
                <div style="color: #558b2f; font-size: 14px;">Your registration is complete and your account is fully operational.</div>
            </div>

            <!-- Credentials Section -->
            <h3 style="color: #704294; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; border-bottom: 2px solid #e9ecef; padding-bottom: 12px; margin-top: 35px; margin-bottom: 20px;">Your Account Credentials</h3>

            <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #faf8ff 0%, #f5f3ff 100%); border-left: 4px solid #704294; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 8px;">
                <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;">
                    <tr>
                        <td style="padding: 12px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef; font-weight: 600; width: 160px; color: #704294;">Email Address:</td>
                        <td style="padding: 12px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef; color: #333;">{{UserEmail}}</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td style="padding: 12px 0; font-weight: 600; color: #704294;">App Secret:</td>
                        <td style="padding: 12px 0; color: #d63384;"><span style="font-family: 'Courier New', monospace; font-weight: 700; background: rgba(214, 51, 132, 0.1); padding: 4px 8px; border-radius: 4px;">{{AppSecret}}</span></td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
            </div>

            <!-- Getting Started Section -->
            <h3 style="color: #704294; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; border-bottom: 2px solid #e9ecef; padding-bottom: 12px; margin-top: 35px; margin-bottom: 20px;">Getting Started</h3>

            <div style="background: linear-gradient(to right, #faf8ff 0%, #ffffff 100%); padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0;">
                <ol style="padding-left: 25px; line-height: 2; color: #495057;">
                    <li><strong style="color: #704294;">Sign In:</strong> Use your email address to access the platform</li>
                    <li><strong style="color: #704294;">Register Applications:</strong> Add your applications that need email services</li>
                    <li><strong style="color: #704294;">Configure SMTP:</strong> Set up your SMTP settings for each application</li>
                    <li><strong style="color: #704294;">Start Sending:</strong> Integrate with our REST API to send emails</li>
                </ol>
            </div>

            <!-- Important Notice -->
            <div style="margin: 25px 0; padding: 16px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff3e0 0%, #ffe0b2 100%); border: 1px solid #ffcc80; border-left: 4px solid #ff9800; border-radius: 8px;">
                <div style="color: #e65100; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 6px;">⚠️ Important Security Notice</div>
                <div style="color: #bf360c; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7;">
                    Keep your App Secret confidential and never share it publicly. For enhanced protection, store credentials in secure vaults such as Azure Key Vault or AWS Secrets Manager, and rotate them periodically.
                </div>
            </div>

            <p style="margin-top: 30px; color: #6c757d;">If you have any questions or need assistance, our dedicated support team is here to help you succeed.</p>

            <p style="margin-top: 25px;">Best regards,<br><strong style="color: #704294;">TPMailer Team</strong></p>
        </div>

        <!-- Footer -->
        <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f7ff 0%, #faf8ff 100%); padding: 25px 30px; text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid #e9ecef;">
            <p style="margin: 0 0 8px 0; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; color: #704294;">TPMailer</p>
            <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 12px; color: #adb5bd;">&copy; {{Year}} All rights reserved.</p>
            <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; font-size: 11px; color: #c0c4cc;">This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
